 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-100 shadow-sm px-4 py-2 mb-6 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold\"><span class=\"text-[var(--color-primary)]\">💻 Technical Excellence</span><span class=\"text-[var(--color-secondary)]\">Scale your business</span></div><h1 class=\"text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-[var(--color-navy)] mb-6 tracking-tight\">Our <span class=\"text-[var(--color-primary)]\">Services</span></h1><p class=\"text-gray-500 max-w-xl mx-auto text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed\">High-performance development, custom design tokens, and result-oriented digital marketing strategies built around your growth objectives.</p></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-16 z-0\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(to top, #ffffff, transparent)\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div></section><section class=\"max-w-[1320px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-8 mb-24\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 shadow-[var(--shadow-card)] hover:border-blue-300 hover:shadow-[var(--shadow-lg)] transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col justify-between group\"><div><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-monitor\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"14\" x=\"2\" y=\"3\" rx=\"2\"></rect><line x1=\"8\" x2=\"16\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"21\"></line><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"17\" y2=\"21\"></line></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-navy)] mb-3\">Web Development</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-6\">Fast, responsive, and secure custom web platforms engineered to scale. We construct highly-optimized sites that load in milliseconds and convert visitors into active customers.</p></div><div class=\"border-t border-gray-50 pt-5 mt-4\"><h4 class=\"text-xs font-bold text-[var(--color-navy)] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">Key Deliverables:</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-[var(--color-secondary)] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Next.js &amp; React Frameworks</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-[var(--color-secondary)] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>CMS Integration (headless/custom)</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-[var(--color-secondary)] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>E-Commerce Architectures</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-[var(--color-secondary)] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Speed &amp; Core Web Vitals optimization</span></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 shadow-[var(--shadow-card)] hover:border-teal-300 hover:shadow-[var(--shadow-lg)] transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col justify-between group\"><div><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-teal-50 text-teal-600 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-smartphone\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"14\" height=\"20\" x=\"5\" y=\"2\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M12 18h.01\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-navy)] mb-3\">Mobile Apps</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-6\">Cross-platform mobile apps built with React Native and Flutter. We provide slick animations, offline data synchronizations, and seamless App Store/Play Store launches.</p></div><div class=\"border-t border-gray-50 pt-5 mt-4\"><h4 class=\"text-xs font-bold text-[var(--color-navy)] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">Key Deliverables:</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-[var(--color-secondary)] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>iOS &amp; Android SDK deployment</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-[var(--color-secondary)] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Secure API Gateway linkages</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-[var(--color-secondary)] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Real-time Push Notifications</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-[var(--color-secondary)] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Local Storage &amp; SQLite DBs</span></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 shadow-[var(--shadow-card)] hover:border-orange-300 hover:shadow-[var(--shadow-lg)] transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col justify-between group\"><div><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-orange-50 text-orange-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-palette\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 22a1 1 0 0 1 0-20 10 9 0 0 1 10 9 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-2.25a1.75 1.75 0 0 0-1.4 2.8l.3.4a1.75 1.75 0 0 1-1.4 2.8z\"></path><circle cx=\"13.5\" cy=\"6.5\" r=\".5\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle><circle cx=\"17.5\" cy=\"10.5\" r=\".5\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle><circle cx=\"6.5\" cy=\"12.5\" r=\".5\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle><circle cx=\"8.5\" cy=\"7.5\" r=\".5\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-navy)] mb-3\">UI/UX &amp; Branding</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-6\">Stunning user interface designs and clear wireframes mapped directly to user personas. We focus on high-fidelity designs, clear typography, and responsive micro-interactions.</p></div><div class=\"border-t border-gray-50 pt-5 mt-4\"><h4 class=\"text-xs font-bold text-[var(--color-navy)] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">Key Deliverables:</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-[var(--color-secondary)] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Figma Design System setup</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-[var(--color-secondary)] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>High-Fidelity Wireframes</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-[var(--color-secondary)] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Interactive Prototyping</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-[var(--color-secondary)] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Corporate Identity Guidelines</span></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 shadow-[var(--shadow-card)] hover:border-purple-300 hover:shadow-[var(--shadow-lg)] transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col justify-between group\"><div><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-purple-50 text-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-cloud\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M17.5 19H9a7 7 0 1 1 6.71-9h1.79a4.5 4.5 0 1 1 0 9Z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-navy)] mb-3\">Digital Marketing</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-6\">Increase your brand visibility and client acquisition. We handle lead generation campaigns, pay-per-click setups, and targeted content strategies to boost conversions.</p></div><div class=\"border-t border-gray-50 pt-5 mt-4\"><h4 class=\"text-xs font-bold text-[var(--color-navy)] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">Key Deliverables:</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-[var(--color-secondary)] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Targeted PPC &amp; Meta Campaigns</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-[var(--color-secondary)] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Lead-Capture Landing Pages</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-[var(--color-secondary)] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Email Automations</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-[var(--color-secondary)] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Performance Analytics &amp; ROIs</span></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 shadow-[var(--shadow-card)] hover:border-green-300 hover:shadow-[var(--shadow-lg)] transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col justify-between group\"><div><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-green-50 text-green-600 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-search\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21 21-4.34-4.34\"></path><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"8\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-navy)] mb-3\">SEO Optimization</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-6\">Elevate your ranking on Google search pages. We audit page structure, metadata, crawl errors, and integrate schema markup for enhanced rich search snippets.</p></div><div class=\"border-t border-gray-50 pt-5 mt-4\"><h4 class=\"text-xs font-bold text-[var(--color-navy)] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">Key Deliverables:</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-[var(--color-secondary)] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Technical &amp; Structural Audits</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-[var(--color-secondary)] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Keyword Cluster Strategies</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-[var(--color-secondary)] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Schema.org Markup injection</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-[var(--color-secondary)] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Google Console integration</span></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 shadow-[var(--shadow-card)] hover:border-pink-300 hover:shadow-[var(--shadow-lg)] transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col justify-between group\"><div><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-pink-50 text-pink-600 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-award\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m15.477 12.89 1.515 8.526a.5.5 0 0 1-.81.47l-3.58-2.687a1 1 0 0 0-1.197 0l-3.586 2.686a.5.5 0 0 1-.81-.469l1.514-8.526\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"6\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-navy)] mb-3\">Branding Solutions</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-6\">Formulate a professional, modern presence that leaves a lasting impression. From logos and brandmarks to business assets, we align your business&#x27;s visual assets with its values.</p></div><div class=\"border-t border-gray-50 pt-5 mt-4\"><h4 class=\"text-xs font-bold text-[var(--color-navy)] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">Key Deliverables:</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-[var(--color-secondary)] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Unique Logo Design</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-[var(--color-secondary)] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Custom Vector Illustration</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-[var(--color-secondary)] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Style Guide &amp; Palette creation</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check text-[var(--color-secondary)] shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span>Digital Asset kits</span></li></ul></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-[var(--color-bg-subtle)] py-20 border-y border-gray-100 mb-20\"><div class=\"max-w-[1320px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-3\"><div class=\"w-8 h-[2px] bg-[var(--color-primary)]\"></div><span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-[var(--color-primary)] tracking-widest uppercase\">How We Deliver</span><div class=\"w-8 h-[2px] bg-[var(--color-primary)]\"></div></div><h2 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[var(--color-navy)] mb-4\">Our Development <span class=\"text-[var(--color-secondary)]\">Lifecycle</span></h2><p class=\"text-gray-500 max-w-md mx-auto text-sm sm:text-base\">A structured execution model to build, review, optimize, and safely launch each project on schedule.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8\"><div class=\"bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm relative group hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300\"><div class=\"absolute top-4 right-4 text-3xl font-black text-gray-100 select-none group-hover:text-blue-50 transition-colors\">01</div><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 text-[var(--color-primary)] flex items-center justify-center mb-5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-compass\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m16.24 7.76-1.804 5.411a2 2 0 0 1-1.265 1.265L7.76 16.24l1.804-5.411a2 2 0 0 1 1.265-1.265z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-base font-bold text-[var(--color-navy)] mb-2\">Discovery &amp; Strategy</h3><p class=\"text-xs sm:text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">We analyze your business targets, target audience, and current digital state to build a complete project plan.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm relative group hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300\"><div class=\"absolute top-4 right-4 text-3xl font-black text-gray-100 select-none group-hover:text-blue-50 transition-colors\">02</div><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 text-[var(--color-primary)] flex items-center justify-center mb-5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-palette\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 22a1 1 0 0 1 0-20 10 9 0 0 1 10 9 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-2.25a1.75 1.75 0 0 0-1.4 2.8l.3.4a1.75 1.75 0 0 1-1.4 2.8z\"></path><circle cx=\"13.5\" cy=\"6.5\" r=\".5\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle><circle cx=\"17.5\" cy=\"10.5\" r=\".5\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle><circle cx=\"6.5\" cy=\"12.5\" r=\".5\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle><circle cx=\"8.5\" cy=\"7.5\" r=\".5\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-base font-bold text-[var(--color-navy)] mb-2\">UI/UX Prototyping</h3><p class=\"text-xs sm:text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">Our design team produces interactive Figma blueprints and layout systems for client feedback.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm relative group hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300\"><div class=\"absolute top-4 right-4 text-3xl font-black text-gray-100 select-none group-hover:text-blue-50 transition-colors\">03</div><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 text-[var(--color-primary)] flex items-center justify-center mb-5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-cpu\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 20v2\"></path><path d=\"M12 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M17 20v2\"></path><path d=\"M17 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h2\"></path><path d=\"M2 17h2\"></path><path d=\"M2 7h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 12h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 17h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 7h2\"></path><path d=\"M7 20v2\"></path><path d=\"M7 2v2\"></path><rect x=\"4\" y=\"4\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" rx=\"2\"></rect><rect x=\"8\" y=\"8\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" rx=\"1\"></rect></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-base font-bold text-[var(--color-navy)] mb-2\">Agile Development</h3><p class=\"text-xs sm:text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">We translate approved designs into scalable, semantic, and highly tested codebase using a monorepo setup.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm relative group hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300\"><div class=\"absolute top-4 right-4 text-3xl font-black text-gray-100 select-none group-hover:text-blue-50 transition-colors\">04</div><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 text-[var(--color-primary)] flex items-center justify-center mb-5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check-big\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335\"></path><path d=\"m9 11 3 3L22 4\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-base font-bold text-[var(--color-navy)] mb-2\">QA &amp; Deployment</h3><p class=\"text-xs sm:text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">After undergoing rigorous speed and compatibility tests, your platform is safely launched on secure global servers.</p></div></div></div></section><section id=\"demo-projects\" class=\"max-w-[1320px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-8 py-12 mb-16 scroll-mt-24\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-3\"><div class=\"w-8 h-[2px] bg-[var(--color-primary)]\"></div><span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-[var(--color-primary)] tracking-widest uppercase\">Portfolio Showcase</span><div class=\"w-8 h-[2px] bg-[var(--color-primary)]\"></div></div><h2 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[var(--color-navy)] mb-4\">Live Demo <span class=\"text-[var(--color-primary)]\">Projects</span></h2><p class=\"text-gray-500 max-w-xl mx-auto text-sm sm:text-base\">Explore some of the high-performance applications we&#x27;ve engineered.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12\"><div class=\"bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-[var(--shadow-card)] transition-all duration-300 group\"><div class=\"h-64 bg-gray-100 relative overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555066931-4365d14bab8c?auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=800&amp;q=80\" alt=\"Demo Project 1\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-black/10 group-hover:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-500\"></div></div><div class=\"p-8\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 rounded-md border border-blue-100\">Next.js</span><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 bg-orange-50 text-orange-600 rounded-md border border-orange-100\">Hono</span><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 bg-teal-50 text-teal-600 rounded-md border border-teal-100\">Cloudflare D1</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-extrabold text-[var(--color-navy)] mb-2\">Apna Library Platform</h3><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6\">A complete seat-booking and student management system tailored specifically for independent study spaces and libraries.</p><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-bold text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:text-[var(--color-secondary)] transition-colors group/link\" href=\"/projects\">View Live Demo <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right group-hover/link:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-[var(--shadow-card)] transition-all duration-300 group\"><div class=\"h-64 bg-gray-100 relative overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1618401471353-b98aedd07871?auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=800&amp;q=80\" alt=\"Demo Project 2\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-black/10 group-hover:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-500\"></div></div><div class=\"p-8\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 rounded-md border border-blue-100\">React</span><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 bg-purple-50 text-purple-600 rounded-md border border-purple-100\">Stripe</span><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 bg-green-50 text-green-600 rounded-md border border-green-100\">Tailwind CSS</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-extrabold text-[var(--color-navy)] mb-2\">Local E-Commerce MVP</h3><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6\">A high-conversion storefront built for rapid deployment. Integrated with Stripe payments and robust inventory tracking.</p><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-bold text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:text-[var(--color-secondary)] transition-colors group/link\" href=\"/projects\">View Live Demo <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right group-hover/link:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div><div class=\"text-center\"><a class=\"btn-cta-green inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold\" href=\"/projects\">View All Projects <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right ml-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></section><section class=\"max-w-[1060px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-8\"><div c